{
  "stem": "25114.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All the Juden, you know, go all to their own places, where they were yesterday, or you will-- or everybody will be dead.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we're trying to run across to our building.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But at the same time, something pulled us back to this-- we were closer to this building.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were sort of afraid to cross, because they were in our way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we run into this building, this one we just came out of, where my sister had those influential friends that could have known something.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we stayed in this building.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they-- the moment we walked in, we wanted to get out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because we thought, everybody in their place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "If they want to find us, they'll say, oh, well, you know, they'll shoot us anyway.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But in this-- this reasoning is-- you act by instinct.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You don't act by reason in this particular case, because you just-- your adrenaline works.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Something-- you're not yourself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You're just some sort of a machine, by instincts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we wanted to run out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then this German with a thing bolted the door and said, nobody comes out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Nobody goes in, nobody goes out!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Here, you stay where you are.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we stayed where we are.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wanted to go into the rooms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was in the corridor before, the door to the entrance of the building, near the door.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we had just come in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We wanted to go to these rooms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, no, there's no room for you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the Germans were here yesterday, and they made a selection.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they counted us, and they said if they found one more person than they counted, they whole room will be dead, will be shot.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they didn't want to let us in.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
